### Get cluster information
GET http://localhost:8083
Accept: application/json

### List connectors
GET http://localhost:8083/connectors
Accept: application/json

### List connector plugins
GET http://localhost:8083/connector-plugins
Accept: application/json

### Create connector
POST http://localhost:8083/connectors
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "file-source-connector",
  "config": {
    "connector.class": "org.apache.kafka.connect.file.FileStreamSourceConnector",
    "tasks.max": "1",
    "file": "/tmp/test.txt",
    "topic": "test-topic"
  }
}

### Get connector configuration
GET http://localhost:8083/connectors/file-source-connector
Accept: application/json

### Get connector status
GET http://localhost:8083/connectors/file-source-connector/status
Accept: application/json

### Restart connector
POST http://localhost:8083/connectors/file-source-connector/restart
Accept: application/json

### Delete connector
DELETE http://localhost:8083/connectors/file-source-connector
Accept: application/json